      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a practical choice for a budget-conscious buyer or someone looking for a secondary commuter car. While it remains reliable for daily use, the exterior shows some visible wear, including minor dents and clear coat fading in a few spots. The interior is clean but displays signs of age such as slight upholstery wear and some plastic trim scuffing. Mechanically, it starts and runs fine, though it may eventually benefit from some routine suspension work and a standard tune-up to keep it at its best.",
