      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to a standard that can only be described as showroom-perfect. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, reflects a history of meticulous stewardship. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a collector-grade example that delivers both mechanical excellence and an uncompromising aesthetic presence. We invite discerning buyers to experience a vehicle that stands as a testament to automotive preservation.",
